        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44509596/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44509596/" class="">第51页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/155962726/" class=" " title="郑小黑">郑小黑</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44509596">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">自然本无所谓真伪，真伪是科学家所分别出来以便利思想的；自然本无所谓善恶，善恶是伦理学家所分出来以规范人类生活的。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-02 11:03</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>自然本无所谓真伪，真伪是科学家所分别出来以便利思想的；自然本无所谓善恶，善恶是伦理学家所分出来以规范人类生活的。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







